### Upgrade FW via SNMP 4x - https://etwiki.sys.comcast.net/display/SMARTINT/QA+Cheat+Sheet
#set the server:    snmpset -v2c -c hDaFHJG7 <CM IP of your XB3> .1.3.6.1.2.1.69.1.3.1.0 a 10.255.246.110
